PROJECT DISCRIPTION


Chatto â€“ Real-Time Chat Application
	A full-stack real-time chat application built using Spring Boot and React,
	featuring JWT-based authentication, protected routes, and WebSocket (STOMP) 
	messaging for live communication.
	
Features
	Authentication & Security
		User registration & login
		JWT access token based authentication
		Secure REST APIs with Spring Security
		Protected frontend routes using token validation
		Automatic logout on token expiration
	
	Real-Time Chat (WebSocket)
		Real-time messaging using WebSocket + STOMP
		Secure WebSocket handshake with JWT validation
		User session tracking via WebSocket interceptors
		Join / leave notifications
		Messages broadcasted to all connected users

	Backend (Spring Boot)
		REST APIs for authentication and user validation
		WebSocket configuration using @EnableWebSocketMessageBroker
		Custom WebSocket Handshake Interceptor for JWT verification
		Centralized exception handling
		MongoDB integration for user persistence
		Clean layered architecture:
			Controller
			Service
			Repository
			DTO
			Security
			


Frontend (React + TypeScript)
	React with TypeScript
	ProtectedRoute implementation
	Axios interceptor for automatic token injection
	Custom React Hook for WebSocket (useChatSocket)
	Real-time UI updates without page refresh
	Message formatting with username display
	Clean component-based structure


	
Tech StackğŸ› ï¸
Backend
	Java
	Spring Boot
	Spring Security
	WebSocket (STOMP)
	JWT
	MongoDB
	Maven

Frontend
